{
  "voice_id": "7kXNOCqiaLdszL0OEXks",
  "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
  "voice_settings": {
    "stability": 0.65,
    "similarity_boost": 0.65,
    "style": 0.0,
    "speed": 1.13,
    "use_speaker_boost": true
  },
  "pronunciation_dictionary_locators": [
    {
      "pronunciation_dictionary_id": "AhK3J8mZDRoShxfoJLk6",
      "version_id": "pFvyQBbxEBKyF7C3IHpy"
    }
  ],
  "inter_chunk_silence_ms": 650,
  "chunks": [
    {
      "index": 0,
      "text": "Two language models running side by side.",
      "checksum": "sha256:fc1d584ce20a7877a34e7be72ae274bae19a6d5579653985a61a1e5b144c2901",
      "wav": "chunk-00.wav",
      "duration": 2.2291156462585033,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 0
    },
    {
      "index": 1,
      "text": "Faster than one running alone. That is not a trick.",
      "checksum": "sha256:82c3534b497f7f225a74db34fa63a422c568725bf67f63e63a268f1eb40e9a35",
      "wav": "chunk-01.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 7
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "text": "That is how the fastest L L Ms ship today.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f0aad72b5053075195dcadaae5fe02985ce776f9eee5249c302512a90d1251b5",
      "wav": "chunk-02.wav",
      "duration": 2.507755102040816,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 17
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "text": "Here is what is actually slow about a normal language model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:70d92f1f14d8defefdc5856f63e8de8c51da82307e00c1f8a2ebac53a821f846",
      "wav": "chunk-03.wav",
      "duration": 3.6687528344671203,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 27
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "text": "You feed it a prompt. It runs one full forward pass.",
      "checksum": "sha256:12962f2badc921f1be7b6249ead8ee33ef5d85fd3320850925debf59d57ff47d",
      "wav": "chunk-04.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 38
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "text": "It produces one token. You append that token.",
      "checksum": "sha256:5239d6b64aa91eab3f8f1e7b8f0776ded395b7df7bad248f61304d794a22d879",
      "wav": "chunk-05.wav",
      "duration": 2.693514739229025,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 49
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "text": "You run the whole model again. For the next token.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c793e4611fe008d3ac58815a32b3f61b1f9b70337a84e10c2428dd93091e5f6f",
      "wav": "chunk-06.wav",
      "duration": 2.8792743764172335,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 57
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "text": "And the next. A seventy billion parameter model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9cb45b29da5be17308d2efb8ca7a2917b689536f49c284a3bac76618f0758e81",
      "wav": "chunk-07.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 67
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "text": "Spinning up. For one word. But here is the thing.",
      "checksum": "sha256:ed9936adfa34ed200124e44c48fb9d03a4da69bfa8c1210f0d492e25da5b7c46",
      "wav": "chunk-08.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 75
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "text": "Most tokens do not need a giant model to predict.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8955a960d659151085f89a515c4ba43d0c50c880edffacc6e74974a8d6a7d12b",
      "wav": "chunk-09.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 85
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "text": "The next word after, why did the chicken, is going to be cross.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9d3d9572d73a4dbde3bf69201f6466d0ae7017684360aef77393edd3631bfe5f",
      "wav": "chunk-10.wav",
      "duration": 3.3901133786848074,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 95
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "text": "A tiny model gets that right. The next word after, the quadratic formula is, every model gets that right.",
      "checksum": "sha256:77a4df045ed31cff2f4702070d67bd83dc5c337c782891e07685ae4fed93f09e",
      "wav": "chunk-11.wav",
      "duration": 6.362267573696145,
      "word_count": 19,
      "words_offset": 108
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "text": "So why are we paying for the giant model on the easy parts.",
      "checksum": "sha256:563c449aec2ddb0490e7d6cb6353d7a5759a9e7e8feceb1d93a86c0ab80a6e99",
      "wav": "chunk-12.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 13,
      "words_offset": 127
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "text": "This is speculative decoding. Published by Google in November 2022.",
      "checksum": "sha256:eef9dbfcb8a89be0fdbdb90367090ab6ac5509fd1b4b9c1aeb69a0e4e557b4ed",
      "wav": "chunk-13.wav",
      "duration": 4.31891156462585,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 140
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "text": "Two models. A small fast draft model. A big slow target model.",
      "checksum": "sha256:af6f38967b6f53e66661a2782185a1ee1f780c618822c831e45cac4925472a02",
      "wav": "chunk-14.wav",
      "duration": 3.575873015873016,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 150
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "text": "The draft model speculates four tokens ahead.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f7d8bd3ce596360585dba439e2c5468420b13a9d6e833c63cb121d4e3184589d",
      "wav": "chunk-15.wav",
      "duration": 2.5541950113378684,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 162
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "text": "Cheap and fast. The target model verifies all four.",
      "checksum": "sha256:38d989f13975d7d7b16d0f3d82667a40239ae03129d63aba0ff4f1d54c919383",
      "wav": "chunk-16.wav",
      "duration": 3.01859410430839,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 169
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "text": "In a single parallel pass. Match the draft.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1a469b5ceacb78d98df0b0f382f5d68b8761ad0115ea2f9a8a83189cdd6729fc",
      "wav": "chunk-17.wav",
      "duration": 2.36843537414966,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 178
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "text": "Accept the tokens. Disagree somewhere. Reject from that point.",
      "checksum": "sha256:1140eacb23345665d557f5c239bd32f1c3c94edb0498860e825718514b11ed61",
      "wav": "chunk-18.wav",
      "duration": 3.7616326530612243,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 186
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "text": "The target corrects it. Either way. Multiple tokens.",
      "checksum": "sha256:c89d3ee575fda381aa3bec8fe6c4d45919e2467f6bad2b9148eee5591fd1a3c1",
      "wav": "chunk-19.wav",
      "duration": 2.972154195011338,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 195
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "text": "For the price of one forward pass. Best case.",
      "checksum": "sha256:89595a688cd95a03993907046c7bcf608949c7d64e8fc56ce73340dfa3771a0d",
      "wav": "chunk-20.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 203
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "text": "K plus one tokens per round. Worst case.",
      "checksum": "sha256:f92b1c6db864c543be0f12da407601cb018670ef9219645f3b50e8dacc796132",
      "wav": "chunk-21.wav",
      "duration": 2.3219954648526078,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 212
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "text": "Still one token. Same as without it. Average.",
      "checksum": "sha256:a07703034abf4bf21819bd4cbcec4b3b23f15ba99b13ff969731cc07e20be5cc",
      "wav": "chunk-22.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 220
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "text": "Two to three times faster. Same output. Identical distribution.",
      "checksum": "sha256:dcead00eb8dc87b8caa94ba048b4ee48cff035c14e49314c4e02beb610e1d36b",
      "wav": "chunk-23.wav",
      "duration": 3.9938321995464854,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 228
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "text": "No quality loss. The original paper proved it on T five X X L.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2af0fbc71ff667094ca95718e937c18d1117ae00468a073fe37306e0d2f847d7",
      "wav": "chunk-24.wav",
      "duration": 3.8080725623582765,
      "word_count": 14,
      "words_offset": 237
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "text": "But the speedup is not constant. Math. Code.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b4aaea0bc48bff09bdc2c4af74e8ff56a5a4d0c51a4f535507ec399e2a1c337a",
      "wav": "chunk-25.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 251
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "text": "Boilerplate. The draft is right almost every time.",
      "checksum": "sha256:20ca26b770c9a395de06bfbbc55cf58a330ec8c0c4b798d444778fcecd23f5dc",
      "wav": "chunk-26.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 259
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "text": "Massive speedup. Creative writing. Open prose.",
      "checksum": "sha256:0b56a3d58b83aa76d98cc5cca338ca406ae184db84767da71fd1884108440874",
      "wav": "chunk-27.wav",
      "duration": 3.0650340136054424,
      "word_count": 6,
      "words_offset": 267
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "text": "Every word branches a hundred ways. The draft guesses wrong.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e40c1722bb80049826d4e1bff529f628b52ae9cecba1110bd9d818ce629a4f4b",
      "wav": "chunk-28.wav",
      "duration": 3.250793650793651,
      "word_count": 10,
      "words_offset": 273
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "text": "The speedup collapses. Same model. Same prompt.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e7d2f3c2a978bae3422ea2c5e9e7818d00c824aee5959f819688c04b6a73145e",
      "wav": "chunk-29.wav",
      "duration": 2.8328344671201813,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 283
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "text": "Different speed depending on what you ask.",
      "checksum": "sha256:aa90c5254623d7cb6dfd5b2f2b10f3ee4cfcc41ace7df050d804799857a547e0",
      "wav": "chunk-30.wav",
      "duration": 2.182675736961451,
      "word_count": 7,
      "words_offset": 290
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "text": "And it is not just a trick anymore. It is becoming architecture.",
      "checksum": "sha256:2232d5783fdf36eb13b6c9954f49ab7f1a545601128c86b3ec39b1a90d941752",
      "wav": "chunk-31.wav",
      "duration": 3.5294331065759637,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 297
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "text": "Google's Gemma 4 ships its own drafter built in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:515f9591a636b91978acee2a8e0778a882f113ac927eeef94e73c35eacf73515",
      "wav": "chunk-32.wav",
      "duration": 2.786394557823129,
      "word_count": 9,
      "words_offset": 309
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "text": "Multi token prediction head. Seventy six million parameters.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9fae41170ef8201eb8a003d7140a41f96294399560d0d7562724e1f9bcb3473a",
      "wav": "chunk-33.wav",
      "duration": 3.622312925170068,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 318
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "text": "Sharing the target model's K V cache. That is speculative decoding evolving.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9cb357706d6eddd30d74d917ae53d4b71b7d30702e57c68c9a8719775360823a",
      "wav": "chunk-34.wav",
      "duration": 4.458231292517007,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 326
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "text": "From an inference hack. Into the model itself.",
      "checksum": "sha256:301df4e43c72769ae6c1560f8189952bbda75b5a78476aee11fb19c06b645d60",
      "wav": "chunk-35.wav",
      "duration": 2.647074829931973,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 338
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "text": "Want to try it today? L M Studio has it built in.",
      "checksum": "sha256:9201b012c932ea0df17d2866aaa6473e320c59d13ec5be18f5e05ac61c40b974",
      "wav": "chunk-36.wav",
      "duration": 3.111473922902494,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 346
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "text": "Load your main model. Pick a smaller draft with the same vocabulary.",
      "checksum": "sha256:206091eee260fbc2df872ba7378056942b983206536335b5ac3aeb073826efb4",
      "wav": "chunk-37.wav",
      "duration": 3.436553287981859,
      "word_count": 12,
      "words_offset": 358
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "text": "Start chatting. For production, v L L M takes one flag.",
      "checksum": "sha256:b15df6aeb3783bf010a180a6e57f31982175831e4b96c8398b44ab7cc3c8b4e5",
      "wav": "chunk-38.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 11,
      "words_offset": 370
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "text": "Pass speculative model and number of speculative tokens.",
      "checksum": "sha256:8dae091018c5267442292b847f59ebc475bb14231e34fe504cd2ac6a61929127",
      "wav": "chunk-39.wav",
      "duration": 3.4829931972789114,
      "word_count": 8,
      "words_offset": 381
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "text": "Same trick. Identical output. So next time someone tells you that you cannot make an L L M faster without losing quality, they are wrong.",
      "checksum": "sha256:e7b7ac939a8e95d116dc4bd055df5bfe0f24ad0b39daedac4c1c698ea94a099f",
      "wav": "chunk-40.wav",
      "duration": 8.870022675736962,
      "word_count": 25,
      "words_offset": 389
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "text": "The math has been here since 2022. If you want to learn more about A I, check out the dynamous A I community.",
      "checksum": "sha256:cb70cbcae311b3a97b9236a34e27f4b0ffec3d919350856038c56d912329aae5",
      "wav": "chunk-41.wav",
      "duration": 6.594467120181406,
      "word_count": 23,
      "words_offset": 414
    }
  ]
}